title: Girl Scout Cookie Rankings, Biden Jazz? 3.6.20
itunes:title: Girl Scout Cookie Rankings, Biden Jazz? 3.6.20
description:
In episode 584, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Blair Socci to discuss Love Is Blind, Chuck Schumer coming for the Supreme Court over abortion laws, Elizabeth Warren dropping out, Biden leading in the polls with his Biden jazz, Americans not trusting the government to take care of the coronavirus, a big upcoming box office opening for Mulan, the new Cinnamon Toast Crunch Coffeemate creamer, Chrissy Teigan's Girl Scout cookie rankings, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. So, We're Probably Going To Lose Some Abortion Rights Soon
  2. Schumer Softens Comments Amid Republicans’ Sustained SCOTUS Outrage
  3. WATCH: Chuck Schumer says Supreme Court Justices Brett Kavanaugh and Neil Gorsuch
  4. Elizabeth Warren, Once a Front-Runner, Drops Out of Presidential Race
  5. Poll: Biden holds massive lead over Sanders in Florida
  6. ‘Biden can finish Bernie off in Michigan’
  7. Politicians Are The Last People Americans Want Fighting Coronavirus
  8. Box Office: ‘Mulan’ Eyes Huge $85 Million-Plus Opening Weekend
  9. Would your coffee be tastier with a Cinnamon Toast Crunch spoon?
  10. Chrissy Teigen’s Girl Scout cookie rankings strike a chord with America
  11. WATCH: Herbie Hancock: Textures
